GENDRON IRON WHEEL CO., Appellant, v. SNOW et al., Respondents. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 3, 1894.) Appeal from special term. Action by the Gendron Iron Wheel Company against Snow, Church & Company.

Argued before DALY, C. J., and BISCHOFF and PRYOR, JJ.

C. H. Fuller, for appellant.

No opinion. Order affirmed, with costs.
